title: Judge tears up district of Republican vying to be House speaker
text: TALLAHASSEE, Fla. (Reuters) - A Florida judge seeking to resolve a long-running legal dispute over the state's congressional districts on Friday sent the state Supreme Court a new map that breaks up the constituency of U.S. Representative Daniel Webster, a Republican vying to become speaker of the House.
